metadata.name: Sakura Falls on the Sunflowers
metadata.description:
Late of springs that night, the city looks different. But Hanae love it so much. Spring is her favorite season.
"Mr Sunflower dolls!". Hanae had one when she was a child.
"The falling sakura looks so beautiful! Everyone should see this!"
"The train station looks very busy tonight. I wonder, are they headed to the same destination? Should I too?". Hanae leaves the train station to enjoy the city once more.

1920 x 1920 | MP4
